lead_paragraph: WASHINGTON, Nov. 13 -- Hjalmar J. Procope, the Finnish Minister, assured Stunner Welles, Under-Secretary of State, at a conference today that he had reported fully and accurately to his government their conversation of last Aug. 18 when Mr. Welles transmitted the Russian suggestion of peace negotiations with Finland.
